News.Title: Canarys Automations Secures 15 Crore Rupees Order
News.Summary: Canarys Automations, a company with a market capitalization of 2.3 billion rupees, has won an order worth 15 crore rupees. The company is listed in the Small and Medium Enterprise (SME) segment.

News.Title: Canarys Automations Secures 55.3 Million Rupee Contract from Infosys Noida
News.Summary: Canarys Automations has been awarded a contract worth 55.3 million rupees by Infosys Noida. This development is significant for Canarys Automations, which is classified as a Small and Medium Enterprise (SME).
